response.original_title: The Life and Times of Gavin Weiland
response.overview: Canadian influencer "Gavin Weiland" (Sam Roberts) has a blowout weekend in Los Angeles before he must return to his 9-to-5 job in Victoria B.C.  3 weeks after we published this video, Sam changed his Instagram handle from "gavinweiland" to "strappnasti." This is an influencer case study.
